projects.description:
Working on AI Matching Engine Project (for True Data Driven Hiring).

More details about the project:
Leverage the power of AI through our proprietary self-learning matching algorithm that gets better over time. With every candidate that passes through Harver, the platform optimizes the factors that are predictive for quality for hire.

Support smart hiring decisions with proven science and data. Harver’s assessments were designed and vetted by industry leading neuroscientists and psychologists.

Briefly tech stack:
• Data Science | Machine Learning: python, numpy, scipy, pandas, python-dotenv, matplotlib, seaborn, jupyter, scikit-learn, R and a lot of magic under the hood);
• Data retrieval and processing: Apache Spark (AWS Glue, EMR), Elastic Search;
• Databases: MongoDB, RDS, S3;
• Architecture: Data lake, Machine Learning, event driven development, SOA/(micro) services, REST APIs;
